nodes.text: The Dustig Trace, also known as the Dustig Trade Route, was a route from Demos Four to the Kath system. From 3701 to 3699 BBY, it was used to jump onto a stable path to the Outer Rim Territories as part of the Seswenna Expansion, eventually becoming part of the future Hydian Way. It also provided a bypass of the Tyus Cluster.
